name: SUPPORT
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - We are held by the Universe.

You are held, the Universe is supporting you, and there are people who support you. Notice who they are, the ones who truly support your becoming and be grateful to them and forgive the ones who don’t. They are indicators along the way of what you need and what is not
useful. What can you do now to support yourself?

Watch for the signs, the things that are working, the smooth moments of flow in your everyday life. There is so much going on behind the scenes, the work of creating and loving and giving. Go deep within yourself to the silence and know that you are held. Release yourself into the nourishing dark quiet. Let your muscles relax and become soft as you let
go into the support.

All is well 

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
